title: Irelands High Court orders investigation into Facebooks transfer of users data to the US
text:
Ireland's High Court orders investigation into Facebook's transfer of users data to the US 
Merco Press Saturday 24th October, 2015 
Ireland’s High Court ordered an investigation into Facebook’s transfer of European Union users’ data to the United States to make sure personal privacy was properly protected from US government surveillance.
